genresAdvancedInfo.name: tijuana electronic
genresAdvancedInfo.description: Tijuana Electronic is a subgenre of electronic music that originated in Tijuana, Mexico. It is characterized by its fusion of traditional Mexican music with electronic beats and rhythms. The music often incorporates elements of cumbia, norte√±o, and banda music, and is known for its high-energy, danceable beats.
